# Address Validation API Documentation
# POST /api/v1/validate-address
# Validates a US address using third-party provider with caching


### Valid Address Example

POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/validate-address HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "1600 Pennsylvania Ave NW, Washington DC 20500"
}


### Expected Response (200 OK)

# {
# "status": "valid",
# "inputAddress": "1600 Pennsylvania Ave NW, Washington DC 20500",
# "standardizedAddress": {
# "streetNumber": "1600",
# "streetName": "Pennsylvania",
# "streetSuffix": "Ave",
# "secondaryDesignator": null,
# "secondaryNumber": null,
# "city": "Washington",
# "state": "DC",
# "zipCode": "20500",
# "zipPlus4": "0003"
# }
# }


