### Invalid Request (Missing Address Field)

POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/validate-address HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "location": "1600 Pennsylvania Ave NW"
}


### Expected Response (400 Bad Request)

# {
# "statusCode": 400,
# "message": "Validation failed",
# "error": "Bad Request"
# }


### Invalid Request (Empty Address)

POST http://localhost:3000/api/v1/validate-address HTTP/1.1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": ""
}


### Expected Response (400 Bad Request)

# {
# "statusCode": 400,
# "message": "Address cannot be empty",
# "error": "Bad Request"
# }


